snippet.title: Multiplying and Dividing Fractions Word Problem: Can You Solve It?
snippet.description:
Can you solve this multiplying and dividing fractions word problem?

This lesson answers the question: Multiplying and Dividing Fractions. How can students interpret division as a unit rate? How can we use a visual fraction model to show a quotient? How can we multiply and divide fractions?

Be sure to join our mailing list at http://www.mashupmath.com
